## üß† Usage Example

```bash
from roadxpert import analyze_road

result = analyze_road(
    image_input="road.jpg",
    latitude=23.341468,
    longitude=86.372060,
    location_name="Purulia, West Bengal"
)

print(result["summary"])

```
